<div class="com-share" data-id="25486" data-title="《高原红小女孩很火，这位日本摄影师又拍了台湾的普通人》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25486/medium/25486.jpg?1460629606" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25486.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
